title: Share your server log
description:
The server log can help finding a lot of information about what is happening in your server, and can help us finding the issue and helping you to fix it.
Make sure you paste the full log

fields.name: Where can i find my server log?
fields.value:: Go to your server directory and look for the logs folder, then select the latest.log

fields.name: You can use this free website to share your log

footer.text:: This embed was sent by a staff member, you can open a ticket for further information.
